file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: '1'
  title: pathLevelParameters
paths:
  /example:
    parameters:
      - in: query
        name: a
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: b
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '204':
          description: example
